## 🎓 v5.8 설계 패턴

### 패턴 1: 카운팅

```rust
fn count_items(items: &[&str]) -> HashMap<&str, usize> {
    let mut counts = HashMap::new();
    for item in items {
        *counts.entry(*item).or_insert(0) += 1;
    }
    counts
}
```

### 패턴 2: 그룹화

```rust
fn group_by<K: Eq + Hash + Clone>(
    items: Vec<(K, String)>,
) -> HashMap<K, Vec<String>> {
    let mut groups = HashMap::new();
    for (key, value) in items {
        groups.entry(key).or_insert_with(Vec::new).push(value);
    }
    groups
}
```

### 패턴 3: 캐시

```rust
struct Cache<K, V> {
    data: HashMap<K, V>,
}

impl<K: Eq + Hash, V: Clone> Cache<K, V> {
    fn get_or_compute<F>(&mut self, key: K, f: F) -> V
    where
        F: Fn(&K) -> V,
    {
        self.data.entry(key.clone())
            .or_insert_with(|| f(&key))
            .clone()
    }
}
```

